transforms.result: # What is git? ## ::left:: Git is a version control system that tracks changes in your files over time. **Key Features**: - Keeps a history of file changes - Lets you save snapshots of your project - Allows you to work in branches - Helps you merge changes - Works locally — no internet required! ::right:: ```mermaid {theme: 'base', scale: 0.8} gitGraph TB: commit id: "version 0.0" commit id: "version 0.1" checkout main branch Steven commit id: "new feature" commit id: "documentation" branch Jane checkout Steven commit id: "fix code" checkout main merge Steven commit id: "version 0.2" checkout Jane commit id: "fix documentation" checkout main merge Jane id: "version 0.4.2" ```
